name: Funny Doggie
description: A simple game of speed and reaction. The funny doggie loves tasty and aromatic bones. The strange hornet throws a favorite doggie treat into nature, and the doggie should not miss any of its favorite treats. Feel free to rate the game and leave comments. The game is free, donation is optional, but if you want, I will not mind, thank you very much :) ------------------------ Game controls: ← - move left → - move right Z - pause mouse ------------------------ Special thanks to all the guys who share their assets !!! Graphics: *RavenTale *Novagoat ------------------------
